{"id": "ros022", "name": "Cam_Kyuu_702_11_20", "res": null, "contents": [[{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Node_Rain"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Gate_Conner", "Gate Opens"], "content": ""}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Member D"], "content": "Chief, the car is ready.\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>... Why is he still there?</i>\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "image", "attrs": ["ros2201"], "content": ""}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[ROBO_Head]"], "content": "<i>......</i>\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Member D"], "content": "Apologies... we just couldn't drive him away. No matter how far we dump him, he would always return and proceed to stand there. It has been several days already...\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Nora"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Member D"], "content": "Send him to another Node?\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>He'll still figure out a way to come back.</i>\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Member D"], "content": "It'll get really ugly if the Mogura people catch wind of this. Maybe we should...\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>Ignore him. We're running short on time. Let's go.</i>\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Member D"], "content": "Yes, Chief.\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[ROBO_Head]"], "content": "<i>......</i>\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[→Signal Switches]</i>\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ryu"], "content": "Calling me to this place... You like to talk business in this kind of rain?\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>Your Butsudou is already tapped by at least two organizations. Do you realize that?</i>\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ryu"], "content": "*Chuckles* Of course I do. Let them hear all they want. Our status in Node 03 as the \"Dragon Phoenix Combo\" is already impregnable. A leaked secret or two won't make much of a difference to us.\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>I don't like to have a third party around when I'm talking.</i>\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ryu"], "content": "Fair enough. Here's the share for this month, as well as the report.\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>Daigo.</i>\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Member D"], "content": "Yes, Chief.\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["ROBO_Scan", "Data transfer"], "content": ""}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ryu"], "content": "This is spectacular. When Phoenix was gone, I previously thought it was going to be a major loss. Turns out you were the greatest treasure all this time. Look at all these numbers.\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Nora"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ryu"], "content": "Thanks to the establishment of the Kyubo Medical Center, not only have we created the biggest business chain this organization has ever seen, but we're also highly revered and respect among the civilians.\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>... The resources allocated to the downtown area and area 11 are not enough.\nI hope that starting next month, the Administration Bureau can increase the resource output to these two areas by at least 10%.</i>\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ryu"], "content": "Still asking for the impossible, eh... Nora, we still have other things we need to tend to. I know the health of the civilians is important, but that's not our main business.\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "A while ago, there was a batch of weapons that should've been smuggled to Node 08. The buyer ended up not receiving the cargo. We temporarily took responsibility for that screw-up in place of you guys. I don't think you are qualified to bargain over this stuff with me right now.\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ryu"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>I may not be able to use my \"eyes\" freely anymore, but I am still very well aware of every single screw-up of yours. I advise you to not try to hide anything from me.</i>\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ryu"], "content": "Alright, alright. I'll take care of this case. You can rest assured on that.\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>I've received the report. All the cargo is here. Besides what I just mentioned, all other guidelines will remain unchanged.</i>\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ryu"], "content": "You've truly become outstanding at this job... Maybe one day you'll surpass me and kick me down from the top.\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>Are you threatening me with that comment?</i>\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ryu"], "content": "Not at all. Why would I?\nThis is a place where profit and ability trump everything else. If someone can come in and break the ceiling that I've failed to crack for so many years, I'd be ecstatic. If me being replaced at the top is what it takes, so be it.\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>Unfortunately, I am not interested in 70% of the businesses you currently have. That day will never arrive.</i>\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ryu"], "content": "Is that so...\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Mogura Member"], "content": "Boss, the amount is correct.\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>Then we'll take our leave. Daigo.</i>\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ryu"], "content": "Ah, right... speaking of \"hiding\", I think the same goes for you too, right?\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Nora"], "content": "......?\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ryu"], "content": "I heard that your pet robot came back?\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Nora"], "content": "......!\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ryu"], "content": "No need to be so tense.\nI'm not the kind of person who holds grudges. Our current partnership is very perfect, and I have no intention to disrupt this relation...\nI'll pretend that I didn't see it. That makes us even.\n"}, {"id": 45, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>... Good. Daigo, start the car. Let's go.</i>\n"}, {"id": 46, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Door_Car", "Car door opens"], "content": ""}, {"id": 47, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ryu"], "content": "... That's right. I'm indeed not that kind of person. However, I can't say as much for the folks who serve under me. They're... a bit hard to control, I'd say.\nYou guys should know what to do, right?\n"}, {"id": 48, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Mogura Member"], "content": "Yes, Boss.\n"}, {"id": 49, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[→Signal Switches]</i>\n"}, {"id": 50, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Gate_Conner", "Gate Opens"], "content": ""}, {"id": 51, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[ROBO_Head]"], "content": "<i>......</i>\n"}, {"id": 52, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Member D"], "content": "Chief, he's still there... What should we do? The things Ryu just said...\n"}, {"id": 53, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>Let's go inside. We still got work to do.</i>\n"}, {"id": 54, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Member D"], "content": "... Yes, Chief.\n"}, {"id": 55, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[Signal Lost]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Node_Rain"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Gate_Conner", "扉が開く"], "content": ""}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["組員 D"], "content": "ボス、車の準備が整いました。\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>……なんで、まだここにいるの。</i>\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "image", "attrs": ["ros2201"], "content": ""}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[ROBO_Head]"], "content": "<i>………</i>\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["組員 D"], "content": "申し訳ありません……\nどんなに遠くに放置しても、ここに戻ってくるんです。\nもうすでに何日もここに立っています……\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Nora"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["組員 D"], "content": "他のNodeに連れて行きますか？\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>どちらにせよ、またここに戻ってくる。</i>\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["組員 D"], "content": "もし土竜にバレたら……\nそれとも……\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>放っておいていい。\nもう時間がない。行こう。</i>\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["組員 D"], "content": "はい。\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[ROBO_Head]"], "content": "<i>………</i>\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[→シグナル切り替え]</i>\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ryu"], "content": "この私をこんなところに呼び出すとは……お前は雨の中商談をする趣味でもあるのか？\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>あなたの仏堂は、2つ以上の組織に盗聴されてる。\n知らないとは言わせない。</i>\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ryu"], "content": "ははは、もちろん知っているさ。\n好きなだけ聞かせてやればいい。\n我々「龍鳳組」がNode03で確立した地位は、今更脅かされることはない。\n奴らに秘密の一つや二つ聞かれたところで、痛くもかゆくもない。\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>私は、自分の話を第三者に聞かれるのは好きじゃない。</i>\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ryu"], "content": "お前の言うことももっともだ。\nこれは今月分だ。それから報告書もある。\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>大吾。</i>\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["組員 D"], "content": "はい。\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["ROBO_Scan", "データ送信"], "content": ""}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ryu"], "content": "くくっ、まったく大したものだ。\nPhoenixがいなくなるのは、我々にとって大きな損失になると思っていたが、お前こそが最大の宝だったな。\nこの数字を見てみろ。\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Nora"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ryu"], "content": "九芒医療のおかげで、組織成立以来の商売の鍵を手に入れただけでなく、市民の崇敬も集めることができた。\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>ダウンタウンとエリア11の資源が不足してる。\n管理局には、来月から、この2つの区域に対して資源の増量をお願いしたい。\n最低でも10％。</i>\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ryu"], "content": "それは難しいな……Nora、私たちはここにだけ資金を割くわけにはいかないのだよ。\n確かに市民の健康は重要だ。\nだが、これは我々の本業ではない。\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>Node08まで運ばれるはずだった武器が、買い手に届かなかった件は、こちらがあなたたちに代わって処理してあげた。\nあなたに私と交渉する資格はないと思うけど。</i>\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ryu"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>もう、好きな時に好きなようにこの「目」を使うことはできないけど、それでもあなたたちのミスは全部把握してる。\n私に隠し事ができると思わない方がいい。</i>\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ryu"], "content": "分かった分かった。\nこの件に関しては私が何とかしよう。\nお前は安心していい。\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>報告書は受け取った。\n荷物は全てここにある。\nさっき言ったこと以外の方針は何も変えなくていい。</i>\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ryu"], "content": "みるみるうちに頭角を現してきているな……いつか私を越えて行くんじゃないか？\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>それは、私を脅してる？</i>\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ryu"], "content": "まさか？\nここは利益と実力が全ての弱肉強食の世界だ。\n誰かが、これまで破られることのなかった壁を破るというのなら、私は逆に喜ばしくも感じるくらいだ。\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>残念だけど、あなたの仕事の内の7割は、私の興味のないものばかり。\nだから、そんな日は来ない。</i>\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ryu"], "content": "そうか……？\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["土竜組員"], "content": "ボス、数は問題ありません。\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>じゃあ、私たちはもう行くから。\n大吾。</i>\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ryu"], "content": "そうだ……「隠し事」、という件で言えば、お互い様じゃないか？\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Nora"], "content": "……？\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ryu"], "content": "お前のペットが帰ってきているそうだな？\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Nora"], "content": "……！\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ryu"], "content": "そう緊張しなくてもいい。\n私は昔のことについてとやかく言うような人間ではない。\n今、お前と私はうまくやっている。\n私はこの関係性を壊したくはないからな……見なかったことにしておこう。\nこれで、お互い様だ。\n"}, {"id": 45, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>……ならいい。大吾、出して。</i>\n"}, {"id": 46, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Door_Car", "車のドアが開く"], "content": ""}, {"id": 47, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ryu"], "content": "……私は、そういう人間ではない。\nだが……私の下の者達はどうかな？\n少々手に余る奴らばかりだ。\nお前たち、何をするべきか分かっているな？\n"}, {"id": 48, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["土竜組員"], "content": "はい。\n"}, {"id": 49, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[→シグナル切り替え]</i>\n"}, {"id": 50, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Gate_Conner", "扉が開く"], "content": ""}, {"id": 51, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[ROBO_Head]"], "content": "<i>………</i>\n"}, {"id": 52, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["組員 D"], "content": "ボス、まだいます……どうしますか？\nさきほど、龍のやつが言ってた……\n"}, {"id": 53, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>早く中に入ろう。\nまだ仕事が残ってる。</i>\n"}, {"id": 54, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["組員 D"], "content": "……はい。\n"}, {"id": 55, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[電波切断]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Node_Rain"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Gate_Conner", "大門開啟"], "content": ""}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["組員 D"], "content": "組長，車備好了。\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>……他為什麼還在？</i>\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "image", "attrs": ["ros2201"], "content": ""}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[ROBO_Head]"], "content": "<i>……。</i>\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["組員 D"], "content": "對不起……我們趕不走他，不管把他搬到多遠的地方他都會一直回來站在那，已經好幾天了……\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Nora"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["組員 D"], "content": "把他送到別的 Node？\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>他還是會想辦法回來的。</i>\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["組員 D"], "content": "如果被土竜的人知道就不好了，還是……\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>別管他。時間不多了，出發。</i>\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["組員 D"], "content": "是。\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[ROBO_Head]"], "content": "<i>……。</i>\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[→切換訊號]</i>\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ryu"], "content": "把我叫來這種地方……妳喜歡在雨中談生意？\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>你的佛堂已經被兩個以上的組織監聽了，你知道嗎？</i>\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ryu"], "content": "呵呵，我當然知道。讓他們聽吧，我們「龍鳳組」現在在 Node 03 的地位已經不可撼動，送他們一、兩個小秘密也無關痛癢。\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>我不喜歡說話的時候有第三者。</i>\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ryu"], "content": "合理。這是這個月的份，還有報表。\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>大吾。</i>\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["組員 D"], "content": "是。\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["ROBO_Scan", "資料傳輸"], "content": ""}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ryu"], "content": "真是不得了，Phoenix 走了，本來以為會是很大的損失，沒想到妳才是最大的寶藏啊。看看這數字。\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Nora"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ryu"], "content": "托九芒醫療的福，不但造就了組織成立以來最大的生意鏈，我們在市民心中也倍受崇敬。\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>……下街和 11 區的資源分配都不夠，我希望下個月開始管理局能針對這兩個區域增加資源的輸出，至少 10%。</i>\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ryu"], "content": "還是那麼強人所難啊……Nora，我們還有其他生意要做，我知道市民的健康很重要，但這不是我們的本業啊。\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>前陣子本來應該走私到 Node 08 的武器，買家後來沒有收到貨，這鍋是我們暫時幫你們扛的。我不覺得你有資格跟我討價還價。</i>\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ryu"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>我或許已經無法隨心所欲使用「眼睛」，但你們出了什麼包我都還是知道，別再想瞞我什麼事。</i>\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ryu"], "content": "好吧好吧，這件事我會處理的，妳放心好了。\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>報告我收到了，貨物都在這裡，除了剛剛說的以外其他方針都不做更動。</i>\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ryu"], "content": "妳真的越來越出色了啊……也許有一天會爬到我頭頂上。\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>這是在威脅我嗎？</i>\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ryu"], "content": "怎麼會？這是個以利益與實力為上的地方，若有人能打破一直以來我無法打破的門檻，我反而該高興。\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>很可惜，你手頭上的生意有七成我都不感興趣，不會有那麼一天的。</i>\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ryu"], "content": "是嗎……？\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["土竜組員"], "content": "老大，數量沒問題。\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>那我們走了，大吾。</i>\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ryu"], "content": "對了……說到「隱瞞」，我想是彼此彼此吧？\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Nora"], "content": "……？\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ryu"], "content": "我聽說妳的寵物機器人回來了？\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Nora"], "content": "……！\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ryu"], "content": "別緊張，我不是個會去記舊仇的人。我們現在的合作很完美，我不想破壞這種關係……我會當作沒看見，這樣我們算扯平了。\n"}, {"id": 45, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>……那就好。大吾，開車。</i>\n"}, {"id": 46, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Door_Car", "引擎啟動"], "content": ""}, {"id": 47, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ryu"], "content": "……沒錯，我的確不是那種人。但我底下的人可就很難說了，他們稍微有點難管呢。\n你們知道該怎麼做了吧？\n"}, {"id": 48, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["土竜組員"], "content": "是。\n"}, {"id": 49, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[→切換訊號]</i>\n"}, {"id": 50, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Gate_Conner", "大門開啟"], "content": ""}, {"id": 51, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[ROBO_Head]"], "content": "<i>……。</i>\n"}, {"id": 52, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["組員 D"], "content": "組長，他還在……怎麼辦？剛才龍說的那些……\n"}, {"id": 53, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>進去吧，還有工作要做。</i>\n"}, {"id": 54, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["組員 D"], "content": "……是。\n"}, {"id": 55, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[訊號中斷]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Node_Rain"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Gate_Conner", "문이 열린다"], "content": ""}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["조직원 D"], "content": "팀장님, 차 정비 끝났습니다.\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>.....저 녀석이 왜 아직도 여기 있는 거지?</i>\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "image", "attrs": ["ros2201"], "content": ""}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[ROBO_Head]"], "content": "<i>...........</i>\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["조직원 D"], "content": "죄송합니다... 저희들이 아무리 옮겨도... 어느 정도 멀어지면 스스로 일어나서 다시 저기로 돌아와 서버리더군요... 이렇게 한지도 벌써 며칠이나 됐습니다.\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Nora"], "content": ".......\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["조직원 D"], "content": "다른 Node로 보내버리실 겁니까?\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>그래도 어떻게 해서든 이리로 돌아오려 하겠지.</i>\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["조직원 D"], "content": "토룡 녀석들에게 들키기라도 하면 꽤 곤란해질 겁니다... 역시...\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>저 녀석은 신경 끄도록. 시간 다 됐다. 출발하자.</i>\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["조직원 D"], "content": "네.\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[ROBO_Head]"], "content": "<i>......</i>\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[→신호 변경]</i>\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ryu"], "content": "날 이런 곳으로 불러내다니... 비 오는 날 거래 얘길 하는 것에 취미라도 들였나?\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>당신의 불당은 이미 두 개 이상의 조직들에게 도청을 당하고 있어. 알고는 있나?</i>\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ryu"], "content": "당연히 알고 있지. 실컷 들으라고 해. 그렇다고 해서 Node 03에서 우리 「용황조(龍鳳組)」 입지가 뒤바뀌거나 하진 않을 테니. 뭐, 저 녀석들에게 비밀 한두 개를 흘린다고 해도 크게 타격은 받는 일은 없을 거다.\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>난 대화할 때 제3자가 껴있는 걸 몹시 싫어하거든.</i>\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ryu"], "content": "나름 합리적인 이유군.\n이건 이번 달 몫, 그리고 이건 이번 달 보고서.\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>Daigo.</i>\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["조직원 D"], "content": "네.\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["ROBO_Scan", "데이터 전송"], "content": ""}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ryu"], "content": "정말 대단해. Phoenix가 가버리고 나선 손실이 꽤 클 것으로 예상했었는데, 네가 이 정도까지 해낼 줄은 생각도 못 했다. 이 숫자를 봐라.\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Nora"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ryu"], "content": "Kyubo 의료 센터는 우리 조직 창립이래로 가장 많은 돈을 벌 수 있는 비즈니스가 되었다. 민심도 얻게 된 건 덤이었지.\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>...아랫길 11구역의 자원은 몹시 부족한 상황이야. 다음 달부터는 관리국에서 두 지역에 공급하는 자원을 더 늘려줬으면 한다. 최소 10% 이상.</i>\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ryu"], "content": "그건 조금 무리일 것 같군... Nora, 우리 조직은 지금, 이 비즈니스 말고도 진행해야 할 사업이 한두 개가 아니다. 물론 시민들의 위생과 건강이 매우 중요하다는 것은 알고 있다. 하지만 그건 우리 본업과는 거리가 좀 있는 일이지.\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>Node 08로 운반 예정이었던 무기들을 클라이언트가 받지 못 했을 때, 우리가 나서서 도움을 줬던 것으로 기억하는데...? 당신이 우리와 협상을 할 처지는 아닌 것 같아.</i>\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ryu"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>지금은 「눈」을 원하고 싶을 때 언제든지 사용할 수 있는 것은 아니더라도, 너희가 저지른 실수 정도는 쉽게 알 수 있어. 그러니 날 속일 생각은 하지 않는 게 좋아.</i>\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ryu"], "content": "그래, 그래~ 알겠다.\n우리가 처리하도록 하지.\n그러니 안심해라.\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>보고서도 받았고 \n물건들도 모두 여기에 있어. \n방금 말한 것 말고도 다른 방침들 역시  바꿀 생각은 하지 말았으면 한다.</i>\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ryu"], "content": "정말 갈수록 물건이 되어 가는 군...\n어쩌면 내 머리 위로 올라설 수 있을 날이 올지도.\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>그건, 위협인가?</i>\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ryu"], "content": "그럴 리가?\n오로지 능력과 실력만으로 판가름되는 이런 약육강식의 세계에서, 누군가 넘지 못할 벽을 넘는다는 건 오히려 즐거워해야할 일이지.\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>실망시켜 미안하지만 네가 하려는 사업의 7할은 전부 내 관심 밖 일이야. 그러니 그럴 날은 오지 않을 거라고 미리 말해두지.</i>\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ryu"], "content": "그래...?\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["토룡 조직원"], "content": "형님, 수량엔 문제 없습니다.\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>우리도 이만 가자, Daigo.</i>\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ryu"], "content": "그렇군... 「숨기고 있는 일」이 있다는 건, 서로에게 해당 사항이려나?\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Nora"], "content": "......?\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ryu"], "content": "네가 폐기했다던 그 로봇이 돌아왔다고 들은 것 같은데?\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Nora"], "content": "......!\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ryu"], "content": "긴장할 필요 없다. 옛날 일로 해코지 같은 거 할 생각은 아니니깐. 현재 우리의 협력은 매우 완벽하게 진행되고 있잖아? 나도 괜히 지금의 관계를 깨버리고 싶은 생각은 아니거든... 그냥 못 본 체 해줄 테니, 이걸로 서로 비긴 셈 쳤으면 하는군.\n"}, {"id": 45, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>...그럼 다행이군. Daigo, 출발해.</i>\n"}, {"id": 46, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Door_Car", "차 문을 연다"], "content": ""}, {"id": 47, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ryu"], "content": "...아까 말한 대로, 난 그런 짓을 저지를 사람이 아니야. 하지만 내 아래 있는 녀석들도 그럴 거라곤 장담할 수 없겠군. 조금 다루기 힘겨운 녀석들이라 말이지....\n너희들, 내가 하는 말이 무슨 뜻인지 잘 알고 있겠지?\n"}, {"id": 48, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["토룡 조직원"], "content": "네! 형님!\n"}, {"id": 49, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[→신호 변경]</i>\n"}, {"id": 50, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Gate_Conner", "문이 열린다"], "content": ""}, {"id": 51, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[ROBO_Head]"], "content": "<i>......</i>\n"}, {"id": 52, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["조직원 D"], "content": "팀장님, 저 녀석이 아직도 저기에...\n방금 용(龍) 녀석이 말한 대로면...\n"}, {"id": 53, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>들어가자.\n아직 할 일이 있으니.</i>\n"}, {"id": 54, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["조직원 D"], "content": "...네.\n"}, {"id": 55, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[신호 중단]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Node_Rain"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Gate_Conner", "大門開啟"], "content": ""}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["組員 D"], "content": "組長，車備好了。\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>……他為什麼還在？</i>\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "image", "attrs": ["ros2201"], "content": ""}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[ROBO_Head]"], "content": "<i>……。</i>\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["組員 D"], "content": "對不起……我們趕不走他，不管把他搬到多遠的地方他都會一直回來站在那，已經好幾天了……\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Nora"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["組員 D"], "content": "把他送到別的 Node？\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>他還是會想辦法回來的。</i>\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["組員 D"], "content": "如果被土竜的人知道就不好了，還是……\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>別管他。時間不多了，出發。</i>\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["組員 D"], "content": "是。\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[ROBO_Head]"], "content": "<i>……。</i>\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[→切換訊號]</i>\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ryu"], "content": "把我叫來這種地方……妳喜歡在雨中談生意？\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>你的佛堂已經被兩個以上的組織監聽了，你知道嗎？</i>\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ryu"], "content": "呵呵，我當然知道。讓他們聽吧，我們「龍鳳組」現在在 Node 03 的地位已經不可撼動，送他們一、兩個小秘密也無關痛癢。\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>我不喜歡說話的時候有第三者。</i>\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ryu"], "content": "合理。這是這個月的份，還有報表。\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>大吾。</i>\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["組員 D"], "content": "是。\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["ROBO_Scan", "資料傳輸"], "content": ""}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ryu"], "content": "真是不得了，Phoenix 走了，本來以為會是很大的損失，沒想到妳才是最大的寶藏啊。看看這數字。\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Nora"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ryu"], "content": "托九芒醫療的福，不但造就了組織成立以來最大的生意鏈，我們在市民心中也倍受崇敬。\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>……下街和 11 區的資源分配都不夠，我希望下個月開始管理局能針對這兩個區域增加資源的輸出，至少 10%。</i>\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ryu"], "content": "還是那麼強人所難啊……Nora，我們還有其他生意要做，我知道市民的健康很重要，但這不是我們的本業啊。\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>前陣子本來應該走私到 Node 08 的武器，買家後來沒有收到貨，這鍋是我們暫時幫你們扛的。我不覺得你有資格跟我討價還價。</i>\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ryu"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>我或許已經無法隨心所欲使用「眼睛」，但你們出了什麼包我都還是知道，別再想瞞我什麼事。</i>\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ryu"], "content": "好吧好吧，這件事我會處理的，妳放心好了。\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>報告我收到了，貨物都在這裡，除了剛剛說的以外其他方針都不做更動。</i>\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ryu"], "content": "妳真的越來越出色了啊……也許有一天會爬到我頭頂上。\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>這是在威脅我嗎？</i>\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ryu"], "content": "怎麼會？這是個以利益與實力為上的地方，若有人能打破一直以來我無法打破的門檻，我反而該高興。\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>很可惜，你手頭上的生意有七成我都不感興趣，不會有那麼一天的。</i>\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ryu"], "content": "是嗎……？\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["土竜組員"], "content": "老大，數量沒問題。\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>那我們走了，大吾。</i>\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ryu"], "content": "對了……說到「隱瞞」，我想是彼此彼此吧？\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Nora"], "content": "……？\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ryu"], "content": "我聽說妳的寵物機器人回來了？\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Nora"], "content": "……！\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ryu"], "content": "別緊張，我不是個會去記舊仇的人。我們現在的合作很完美，我不想破壞這種關係……我會當作沒看見，這樣我們算扯平了。\n"}, {"id": 45, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>……那就好。大吾，開車。</i>\n"}, {"id": 46, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Door_Car", "引擎啟動"], "content": ""}, {"id": 47, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ryu"], "content": "……沒錯，我的確不是那種人。但我底下的人可就很難說了，他們稍微有點難管呢。\n你們知道該怎麼做了吧？\n"}, {"id": 48, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["土竜組員"], "content": "是。\n"}, {"id": 49, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[→切換訊號]</i>\n"}, {"id": 50, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Gate_Conner", "大門開啟"], "content": ""}, {"id": 51, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[ROBO_Head]"], "content": "<i>……。</i>\n"}, {"id": 52, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["組員 D"], "content": "組長，他還在……怎麼辦？剛才龍說的那些……\n"}, {"id": 53, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>進去吧，還有工作要做。</i>\n"}, {"id": 54, "type": "conversation", "